{"tid":2053291,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"近 30 年最慘！印度蝗蟲蔽日，毀 5 萬頃農地，雨季恐加速繁殖","createTime":"2020-06-06T07:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T07:36:46.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1bdfae1654077ed79fb412256425bff8d64c28c4","tid":2053291,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:16:27.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情導致印度 1 億人失業，政府竭力應付疫情之際，當地又出現將近 30 年來最嚴重的蝗災，過去 4 週至少有 5 萬公頃農地遭毀。<br />\n<br />\nArab News、Sky News 報導，印度民眾 Suresh Kumar 住在拉賈斯坦邦（Rajasthan）的齋浦爾（Jaipur），有天他在自家陽台喝茶時，突然發現太陽消失了，他原本以為烏雲蔽日，抬頭一看才發現黑鴉鴉的蝗蟲大軍鋪天蓋地而來，遮蔽了整個天際。幾分鐘後，蝗蟲軍團抵達，放眼所及全是蝗蟲，大家嚇到跑進屋裡避難。Kumar 說：「從來沒看過這種事，突然間幾百萬隻蝗蟲入侵，社區有居民敲鑼打鼓想嚇跑蝗蟲，不過沒太大效果。」<br />\n<br />\n1 千公里外的印度中央邦（Madhya Pradesh）巴拉加特（Balaghat）也有類似情況，當地農民 Dev Singh 說，蝗蟲不只佔據了農舍，田裡剛萌芽的豆苗也被摧毀。當地媒體報導，過去 4 週來，這兩邦已有 5 萬公頃農田遭毀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/06/05/india-locust-disaster-is-worst-in-nearly-30-years/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F06%2F05%2Findia-locust-disaster-is-worst-in-nearly-30-years%2F&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=9de278c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/06/05/india-locust-disaster-is-worst-in-nearly-30-years/</a>"},{"pid":"106b8e5167d14b8b1d76a45f18a21ef8918e6f89","tid":2053291,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:18:33.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲來了蘑菇帶路"},{"pid":"60d35cf0277fad1e1353cc1f31be8f3b3759a601","tid":2053291,"uid":283700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:18:48.000Z","msg":"往北趕"},{"pid":"aaef439634e47279a5c678dba5f69a16e1b05b6a","tid":2053291,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"要向中國買農產品了"},{"pid":"30c8e4416147e04a3e94230c554c8a6e6a36b5fb","tid":2053291,"uid":256143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"仲唔對支那開戰去轉移國民視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a15f39029383436446f4e9b7d035e00845cbc8","tid":2053291,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aaef439634e47279a5c678dba5f69a16e1b05b6a","tid":2053291,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"要向中國買農產品了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:36:46.000Z","msg":"支那自己都要入人地貨,你叫印度向支那買農產品?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}